author: Kelly McClure
title: Prince's New Instagram Account Is Incredible
text:
Whoever is running Prince's Instagram account (Prince? Is it really you?) is really using it to its full potential. PRINCESTAGRAM has been up for only three days as of the time of this post, and it's already our new favorite account in a major way. It's chock-full of photos of Prince...and memes...and more photos of Prince. Here are a few of the best shots so far.
Can't look away. What is...I mean...what?
CHOCOLATE OVERDOSE
A photo posted by PRINCESTAGRAM (@prince) on
Oct 22, 2015 at 4:20pm PDT
Wait. Prince likes to binge on Popecorn too?!
B&W
A photo posted by PRINCESTAGRAM (@prince) on
Oct 22, 2015 at 1:52pm PDT
Looking SO good here.
CLOSE UP
A photo posted by PRINCESTAGRAM (@prince) on
Oct 22, 2015 at 3:25pm PDT
"Here's my chair. It's right here."
A photo posted by PRINCESTAGRAM (@prince) on
Oct 22, 2015 at 5:59pm PDT
Bonus Prince related news worth sharing: Did you know that SNL alum Maya Rudolph and her pal Gretchen Lieberum have a Prince cover band called Princess that tours Los Angeles from time to time? Well now you do. Let's hope they turn up on PRINCESTAGRAM some time soon.
